93 template<int DEPTH> struct NppTypeTraits;
94 template<> struct NppTypeTraits<CV_8U> { typedef Npp8u npp_t; };
95 template<> struct NppTypeTraits<CV_8S> { typedef Npp8s npp_t; };
96 template<> struct NppTypeTraits<CV_16U> { typedef Npp16u npp_t; };
97 template<> struct NppTypeTraits<CV_16S> { typedef Npp16s npp_t; typedef Npp16sc npp_complex_type; };
98 template<> struct NppTypeTraits<CV_32S> { typedef Npp32s npp_t; typedef Npp32sc npp_complex_type; };
99 template<> struct NppTypeTraits<CV_32F> { typedef Npp32f npp_t; typedef Npp32fc npp_complex_type; };
100 template<> struct NppTypeTraits<CV_64F> { typedef Npp64f npp_t; typedef Npp64fc npp_complex_type; };
101
102 template<int DEPTH, int cn> struct NppArithmScalarFunc
103 {
104 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_t npp_t;
105
106 typedef NppStatus (*func_ptr)(const npp_t* pSrc1, int nSrc1Step, const npp_t* pConstants,
107 npp_t* pDst, int nDstStep, NppiSize oSizeROI, int nScaleFactor);
108 };
109 template<int DEPTH> struct NppArithmScalarFunc<DEPTH, 1>
110 {
111 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_t npp_t;
112
113 typedef NppStatus (*func_ptr)(const npp_t* pSrc1, int nSrc1Step, const npp_t pConstants,
114 npp_t* pDst, int nDstStep, NppiSize oSizeROI, int nScaleFactor);
115 };
116 template<int DEPTH> struct NppArithmScalarFunc<DEPTH, 2>
117 {
118 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_complex_type npp_complex_type;
119
120 typedef NppStatus (*func_ptr)(const npp_complex_type* pSrc1, int nSrc1Step, const npp_complex_type pConstants,
121 npp_complex_type* pDst, int nDstStep, NppiSize oSizeROI, int nScaleFactor);
122 };
123 template<int cn> struct NppArithmScalarFunc<CV_32F, cn>
124 {
125 typedef NppStatus (*func_ptr)(const Npp32f* pSrc1, int nSrc1Step, const Npp32f* pConstants, Npp32f* pDst, int nDstStep, NppiSize oSizeROI);
126 };
127 template<> struct NppArithmScalarFunc<CV_32F, 1>
128 {
129 typedef NppStatus (*func_ptr)(const Npp32f* pSrc1, int nSrc1Step, const Npp32f pConstants, Npp32f* pDst, int nDstStep, NppiSize oSizeROI);
130 };
131 template<> struct NppArithmScalarFunc<CV_32F, 2>
132 {
133 typedef NppStatus (*func_ptr)(const Npp32fc* pSrc1, int nSrc1Step, const Npp32fc pConstants, Npp32fc* pDst, int nDstStep, NppiSize oSizeROI);
134 };
135
136 template<int DEPTH, int cn, typename NppArithmScalarFunc<DEPTH, cn>::func_ptr func> struct NppArithmScalar
137 {
138 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_t npp_t;
139
140 static void call(const PtrStepSzb src, Scalar sc, PtrStepb dst, cudaStream_t stream)
141 {
142 NppStreamHandler h(stream);
143
144 NppiSize sz;
145 sz.width = src.cols;
146 sz.height = src.rows;
147
148 const npp_t pConstants[] = { saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[0]), saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[1]), saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[2]), saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[3]) };
149
150 nppSafeCall( func((const npp_t*)src.data, static_cast<int>(src.step), pConstants, (npp_t*)dst.data, static_cast<int>(dst.step), sz, 0) );
151
152 if (stream == 0)
153 cudaSafeCall( cudaDeviceSynchronize() );
154 }
155 };
156 template<int DEPTH, typename NppArithmScalarFunc<DEPTH, 1>::func_ptr func> struct NppArithmScalar<DEPTH, 1, func>
157 {
158 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_t npp_t;
159
160 static void call(const PtrStepSzb src, Scalar sc, PtrStepb dst, cudaStream_t stream)
161 {
162 NppStreamHandler h(stream);
163
164 NppiSize sz;
165 sz.width = src.cols;
166 sz.height = src.rows;
167
168 nppSafeCall( func((const npp_t*)src.data, static_cast<int>(src.step), saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[0]), (npp_t*)dst.data, static_cast<int>(dst.step), sz, 0) );
169
170 if (stream == 0)
171 cudaSafeCall( cudaDeviceSynchronize() );
172 }
173 };
174 template<int DEPTH, typename NppArithmScalarFunc<DEPTH, 2>::func_ptr func> struct NppArithmScalar<DEPTH, 2, func>
175 {
176 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_t npp_t;
177 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_complex_type npp_complex_type;
178
179 static void call(const PtrStepSzb src, Scalar sc, PtrStepb dst, cudaStream_t stream)
180 {
181 NppStreamHandler h(stream);
182
183 NppiSize sz;
184 sz.width = src.cols;
185 sz.height = src.rows;
186
187 npp_complex_type nConstant;
188 nConstant.re = saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[0]);
189 nConstant.im = saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[1]);
190
191 nppSafeCall( func((const npp_complex_type*)src.data, static_cast<int>(src.step), nConstant,
192 (npp_complex_type*)dst.data, static_cast<int>(dst.step), sz, 0) );
193
194 if (stream == 0)
195 cudaSafeCall( cudaDeviceSynchronize() );
196 }
197 };
198 template<int cn, typename NppArithmScalarFunc<CV_32F, cn>::func_ptr func> struct NppArithmScalar<CV_32F, cn, func>
199 {
200 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<CV_32F>::npp_t npp_t;
201
202 static void call(const PtrStepSzb src, Scalar sc, PtrStepb dst, cudaStream_t stream)
203 {
204 NppStreamHandler h(stream);
205
206 NppiSize sz;
207 sz.width = src.cols;
208 sz.height = src.rows;
209
210 const Npp32f pConstants[] = { saturate_cast<Npp32f>(sc.val[0]), saturate_cast<Npp32f>(sc.val[1]), saturate_cast<Npp32f>(sc.val[2]), saturate_cast<Npp32f>(sc.val[3]) };
211
212 nppSafeCall( func((const npp_t*)src.data, static_cast<int>(src.step), pConstants, (npp_t*)dst.data, static_cast<int>(dst.step), sz) );
213
214 if (stream == 0)
215 cudaSafeCall( cudaDeviceSynchronize() );
216 }
217 };
218 template<typename NppArithmScalarFunc<CV_32F, 1>::func_ptr func> struct NppArithmScalar<CV_32F, 1, func>
219 {
220 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<CV_32F>::npp_t npp_t;
221
222 static void call(const PtrStepSzb src, Scalar sc, PtrStepb dst, cudaStream_t stream)
223 {
224 NppStreamHandler h(stream);
225
226 NppiSize sz;
227 sz.width = src.cols;
228 sz.height = src.rows;
229
230 nppSafeCall( func((const npp_t*)src.data, static_cast<int>(src.step), saturate_cast<Npp32f>(sc.val[0]), (npp_t*)dst.data, static_cast<int>(dst.step), sz) );
231
232 if (stream == 0)
233 cudaSafeCall( cudaDeviceSynchronize() );
234 }
235 };
236 template<typename NppArithmScalarFunc<CV_32F, 2>::func_ptr func> struct NppArithmScalar<CV_32F, 2, func>
237 {
238 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<CV_32F>::npp_t npp_t;
239 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<CV_32F>::npp_complex_type npp_complex_type;
240
241 static void call(const PtrStepSzb src, Scalar sc, PtrStepb dst, cudaStream_t stream)
242 {
243 NppStreamHandler h(stream);
244
245 NppiSize sz;
246 sz.width = src.cols;
247 sz.height = src.rows;
248
249 Npp32fc nConstant;
250 nConstant.re = saturate_cast<Npp32f>(sc.val[0]);
251 nConstant.im = saturate_cast<Npp32f>(sc.val[1]);
252
253 nppSafeCall( func((const npp_complex_type*)src.data, static_cast<int>(src.step), nConstant, (npp_complex_type*)dst.data, static_cast<int>(dst.step), sz) );
254
255 if (stream == 0)
256 cudaSafeCall( cudaDeviceSynchronize() );

273void cv::gpu::add(const GpuMat& src1, const GpuMat& src2, GpuMat& dst, const GpuMat& mask, int dtype, Stream& s)
274{
275 using namespace arithm;
276
277 typedef void (*func_t)(PtrStepSzb src1, PtrStepSzb src2, PtrStepSzb dst, PtrStepb mask, cudaStream_t stream);
278
279#ifdef OPENCV_TINY_GPU_MODULE
280 static const func_t funcs[7][7] =
281 {
282 {
283 addMat<unsigned char, unsigned char>,
284 0/*addMat<unsigned char, signed char>*/,
285 0/*addMat<unsigned char, unsigned short>*/,
286 0/*addMat<unsigned char, short>*/,
287 0/*addMat<unsigned char, int>*/,
288 0/*addMat<unsigned char, float>*/,
289 0/*addMat<unsigned char, double>*/,
290 },
291 {
292 0/*addMat<signed char, unsigned char>*/,
293 0/*addMat<signed char, signed char>*/,
294 0/*addMat<signed char, unsigned short>*/,
295 0/*addMat<signed char, short>*/,
296 0/*addMat<signed char, int>*/,
297 0/*addMat<signed char, float>*/,
298 0/*addMat<signed char, double>*/,
299 },
300 {
301 0 /*addMat<unsigned short, unsigned char>*/,
302 0 /*addMat<unsigned short, signed char>*/,
303 0/*addMat<unsigned short, unsigned short>*/,
304 0/*addMat<unsigned short, short>*/,
305 0/*addMat<unsigned short, int>*/,
306 0/*addMat<unsigned short, float>*/,
307 0/*addMat<unsigned short, double>*/,
308 },
309 {
310 0 /*addMat<short, unsigned char>*/,
311 0 /*addMat<short, signed char>*/,
312 0/*addMat<short, unsigned short>*/,
313 0/*addMat<short, short>*/,
314 0/*addMat<short, int>*/,
315 0/*addMat<short, float>*/,
316 0/*addMat<short, double>*/,
317 },
318 {
319 0 /*addMat<int, unsigned char>*/,
320 0 /*addMat<int, signed char>*/,
321 0 /*addMat<int, unsigned short>*/,
322 0 /*addMat<int, short>*/,
323 0/*addMat<int, int>*/,
324 0/*addMat<int, float>*/,
325 0/*addMat<int, double>*/,
326 },
327 {
328 0 /*addMat<float, unsigned char>*/,
329 0 /*addMat<float, signed char>*/,
330 0 /*addMat<float, unsigned short>*/,
331 0 /*addMat<float, short>*/,
332 0 /*addMat<float, int>*/,
333 addMat<float, float>,
334 0/*addMat<float, double>*/,
335 },
336 {
337 0 /*addMat<double, unsigned char>*/,
338 0 /*addMat<double, signed char>*/,
339 0 /*addMat<double, unsigned short>*/,
340 0 /*addMat<double, short>*/,
341 0 /*addMat<double, int>*/,
342 0 /*addMat<double, float>*/,
343 0/*addMat<double, double>*/,
344 }
345 };
346#else
347 static const func_t funcs[7][7] =
348 {
349 {
350 addMat<unsigned char, unsigned char>,
351 addMat<unsigned char, signed char>,
352 addMat<unsigned char, unsigned short>,
353 addMat<unsigned char, short>,
354 addMat<unsigned char, int>,
355 addMat<unsigned char, float>,
356 addMat<unsigned char, double>,
357 },
358 {
359 addMat<signed char, unsigned char>,
360 addMat<signed char, signed char>,
361 addMat<signed char, unsigned short>,
362 addMat<signed char, short>,
363 addMat<signed char, int>,
364 addMat<signed char, float>,
365 addMat<signed char, double>,
366 },
367 {
368 0 /*addMat<unsigned short, unsigned char>*/,
369 0 /*addMat<unsigned short, signed char>*/,
370 addMat<unsigned short, unsigned short>,
371 addMat<unsigned short, short>,
372 addMat<unsigned short, int>,
373 addMat<unsigned short, float>,
374 addMat<unsigned short, double>,
375 },
376 {
377 0 /*addMat<short, unsigned char>*/,
378 0 /*addMat<short, signed char>*/,
379 addMat<short, unsigned short>,
380 addMat<short, short>,
381 addMat<short, int>,
382 addMat<short, float>,
383 addMat<short, double>,
384 },
385 {
386 0 /*addMat<int, unsigned char>*/,
387 0 /*addMat<int, signed char>*/,
388 0 /*addMat<int, unsigned short>*/,
389 0 /*addMat<int, short>*/,
390 addMat<int, int>,
391 addMat<int, float>,
392 addMat<int, double>,
393 },
394 {
395 0 /*addMat<float, unsigned char>*/,
396 0 /*addMat<float, signed char>*/,
397 0 /*addMat<float, unsigned short>*/,
398 0 /*addMat<float, short>*/,
399 0 /*addMat<float, int>*/,
400 addMat<float, float>,
401 addMat<float, double>,
402 },
403 {
404 0 /*addMat<double, unsigned char>*/,
405 0 /*addMat<double, signed char>*/,
406 0 /*addMat<double, unsigned short>*/,
407 0 /*addMat<double, short>*/,
408 0 /*addMat<double, int>*/,
409 0 /*addMat<double, float>*/,
410 addMat<double, double>,
411 }
412 };
413#endif
414
415 if (dtype < 0)
416 dtype = src1.depth();
417
418 const int sdepth = src1.depth();
419 const int ddepth = CV_MAT_DEPTH(dtype);
420 const int cn = src1.channels();
421
422 CV_Assert( sdepth <= CV_64F && ddepth <= CV_64F );
423 CV_Assert( src2.type() == src1.type() && src2.size() == src1.size() );
424 CV_Assert( mask.empty() || (cn == 1 && mask.size() == src1.size() && mask.type() == CV_8U) );
425
426 if (sdepth == CV_64F || ddepth == CV_64F)
427 {
428 if (!deviceSupports(NATIVE_DOUBLE))
429 CV_Error(CV_StsUnsupportedFormat, "The device doesn't support double");
430 }
431
432 dst.create(src1.size(), CV_MAKE_TYPE(ddepth, cn));
433
434 cudaStream_t stream = StreamAccessor::getStream(s);
435
436 PtrStepSzb src1_(src1.rows, src1.cols * cn, src1.data, src1.step);
437 PtrStepSzb src2_(src1.rows, src1.cols * cn, src2.data, src2.step);
438 PtrStepSzb dst_(src1.rows, src1.cols * cn, dst.data, dst.step);
439
440 if (mask.empty() && (sdepth == CV_8U || sdepth == CV_16U) && ddepth == sdepth)
441 {
442 const intptr_t src1ptr = reinterpret_cast<intptr_t>(src1_.data);
443 const intptr_t src2ptr = reinterpret_cast<intptr_t>(src2_.data);
444 const intptr_t dstptr = reinterpret_cast<intptr_t>(dst_.data);
445
446 const bool isAllAligned = (src1ptr & 31) == 0 && (src2ptr & 31) == 0 && (dstptr & 31) == 0;
447
448 if (isAllAligned)
449 {
450 if (sdepth == CV_8U && (src1_.cols & 3) == 0)
451 {
452 const int vcols = src1_.cols >> 2;
453
454 addMat_v4(PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) src1_.data, src1_.step),
455 PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) src2_.data, src2_.step),
456 PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) dst_.data, dst_.step),
457 stream);
458
459 return;
460 }
461 else if (sdepth == CV_16U && (src1_.cols & 1) == 0)
462 {
463 const int vcols = src1_.cols >> 1;
464
465 addMat_v2(PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) src1_.data, src1_.step),
466 PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) src2_.data, src2_.step),
467 PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) dst_.data, dst_.step),
468 stream);
469
470 return;
471 }
472 }
473 }
474
475 const func_t func = funcs[sdepth][ddepth];
476
477 if (!func)
478 CV_Error(CV_StsUnsupportedFormat, "Unsupported combination of source and destination types");
479
480 func(src1_, src2_, dst_, mask, stream);
481}

490{
491 using namespace arithm;
492
493 typedef void (*func_t)(PtrStepSzb src1, double val, PtrStepSzb dst, PtrStepb mask, cudaStream_t stream);
494
495#ifdef OPENCV_TINY_GPU_MODULE
496 static const func_t funcs[7][7] =
497 {

499 addScalar<unsigned char, float, unsigned char>,
500 0/*addScalar<unsigned char, float, signed char>*/,

506 },
507 {

515 },

2558
2559void cv::gpu::compare(const GpuMat& src1, const GpuMat& src2, GpuMat& dst, int cmpop, Stream& s)
2560{
2561 using namespace arithm;
2562
2563 typedef void (*func_t)(PtrStepSzb src1, PtrStepSzb src2, PtrStepSzb dst, cudaStream_t stream);
2564
2565#ifdef OPENCV_TINY_GPU_MODULE
2566 static const func_t funcs[7][4] =
2567 {
2568 {cmpMatEq<unsigned char> , cmpMatNe<unsigned char> , cmpMatLt<unsigned char> , cmpMatLe<unsigned char> },
2569 {0, 0, 0, 0},
2570 {0, 0, 0, 0},
2571 {0, 0, 0, 0},
2572 {0, 0, 0, 0},
2573 {cmpMatEq<float> , cmpMatNe<float> , cmpMatLt<float> , cmpMatLe<float> },
2574 {0, 0, 0, 0},
2575 };
2576#else
2577 static const func_t funcs[7][4] =
2578 {
2579 {cmpMatEq<unsigned char> , cmpMatNe<unsigned char> , cmpMatLt<unsigned char> , cmpMatLe<unsigned char> },
2580 {cmpMatEq<signed char> , cmpMatNe<signed char> , cmpMatLt<signed char> , cmpMatLe<signed char> },
2581 {cmpMatEq<unsigned short>, cmpMatNe<unsigned short>, cmpMatLt<unsigned short>, cmpMatLe<unsigned short>},
2582 {cmpMatEq<short> , cmpMatNe<short> , cmpMatLt<short> , cmpMatLe<short> },
2583 {cmpMatEq<int> , cmpMatNe<int> , cmpMatLt<int> , cmpMatLe<int> },
2584 {cmpMatEq<float> , cmpMatNe<float> , cmpMatLt<float> , cmpMatLe<float> },
2585 {cmpMatEq<double> , cmpMatNe<double> , cmpMatLt<double> , cmpMatLe<double> }
2586 };
2587#endif
2588
2589 typedef void (*func_v4_t)(PtrStepSz<unsigned int> src1, PtrStepSz<unsigned int> src2, PtrStepSz<unsigned int> dst, cudaStream_t stream);
2590 static const func_v4_t funcs_v4[] =
2591 {
2592 cmpMatEq_v4, cmpMatNe_v4, cmpMatLt_v4, cmpMatLe_v4
2593 };
2594
2595 const int depth = src1.depth();
2596 const int cn = src1.channels();
2597
2598 CV_Assert( depth <= CV_64F );
2599 CV_Assert( src2.size() == src1.size() && src2.type() == src1.type() );
2600 CV_Assert( cmpop >= CMP_EQ && cmpop <= CMP_NE );
2601
2602 if (depth == CV_64F)
2603 {
2604 if (!deviceSupports(NATIVE_DOUBLE))
2605 CV_Error(CV_StsUnsupportedFormat, "The device doesn't support double");
2606 }
2607
2608 static const int codes[] =
2609 {
2610 0, 2, 3, 2, 3, 1
2611 };
2612 const GpuMat* psrc1[] =
2613 {
2614 &src1, &src2, &src2, &src1, &src1, &src1
2615 };
2616 const GpuMat* psrc2[] =
2617 {
2618 &src2, &src1, &src1, &src2, &src2, &src2
2619 };
2620
2621 const int code = codes[cmpop];
2622
2623 const func_t func = funcs[depth][code];
2624 if (!func)
2625 CV_Error(CV_StsUnsupportedFormat, "Unsupported combination of source and destination types");
2626
2627 dst.create(src1.size(), CV_MAKE_TYPE(CV_8U, cn));
2628
2629 cudaStream_t stream = StreamAccessor::getStream(s);
2630
2631 PtrStepSzb src1_(src1.rows, src1.cols * cn, psrc1[cmpop]->data, psrc1[cmpop]->step);
2632 PtrStepSzb src2_(src1.rows, src1.cols * cn, psrc2[cmpop]->data, psrc2[cmpop]->step);
2633 PtrStepSzb dst_(src1.rows, src1.cols * cn, dst.data, dst.step);
2634
2635 if (depth == CV_8U && (src1_.cols & 3) == 0)
2636 {
2637 const intptr_t src1ptr = reinterpret_cast<intptr_t>(src1_.data);
2638 const intptr_t src2ptr = reinterpret_cast<intptr_t>(src2_.data);
2639 const intptr_t dstptr = reinterpret_cast<intptr_t>(dst_.data);
2640
2641 const bool isAllAligned = (src1ptr & 31) == 0 && (src2ptr & 31) == 0 && (dstptr & 31) == 0;
2642
2643 if (isAllAligned)
2644 {
2645 const int vcols = src1_.cols >> 2;
2646
2647 funcs_v4[code](PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) src1_.data, src1_.step),
2648 PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) src2_.data, src2_.step),
2649 PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) dst_.data, dst_.step),
2650 stream);
2651
2652 return;
2653 }
2654 }
2655
2656 func(src1_, src2_, dst_, stream);
2657}

2751//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
2752// Unary bitwise logical operations
2753
2754namespace arithm
2755{
2756 template <typename T> void bitMatNot(PtrStepSzb src, PtrStepSzb dst, PtrStepb mask, int num_channels, cudaStream_t stream);
2757}
2758
2759void cv::gpu::bitwise_not(const GpuMat& src, GpuMat& dst, const GpuMat& mask, Stream& s)
2760{
2761 using namespace arithm;
2762
2763 const int depth = src.depth();
2764
2765 CV_Assert( depth < CV_32F );
2766 CV_Assert( mask.empty() || (mask.type() == CV_8UC1 && mask.size() == src.size()) );
2767
2768 dst.create(src.size(), src.type());
2769
2770 cudaStream_t stream = StreamAccessor::getStream(s);
2771
2772 if (mask.empty())
2773 {
2774 const int bcols = (int) (src.cols * src.elemSize());
2775 bool aligned =
2776 isAligned(src.data, sizeof(unsigned int)) &&
2777 isAligned(dst.data, sizeof(unsigned int));
2778
2779 if (aligned && (bcols & 3) == 0)
2780 {
2781 const int vcols = bcols >> 2;
2782
2783 bitMatNot<unsigned int>(
2784 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, vcols, src.data, src.step),
2785 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, vcols, dst.data, dst.step),
2786 PtrStepb(), 1, stream);
2787 }
2788 else if (aligned && (bcols & 1) == 0)
2789 {
2790 const int vcols = bcols >> 1;
2791
2792 bitMatNot<unsigned short>(
2793 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, vcols, src.data, src.step),
2794 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, vcols, dst.data, dst.step),
2795 PtrStepb(), 1, stream);
2796 }
2797 else
2798 {
2799 bitMatNot<unsigned char>(
2800 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, bcols, src.data, src.step),
2801 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, bcols, dst.data, dst.step),
2802 PtrStepb(), 1, stream);
2803 }
2804 }
2805 else
2806 {
2807 const int elem_size = static_cast<int>(src.elemSize1());
2808 const int num_channels = src.channels();
2809 const int bcols = src.cols * num_channels;
2810
2811 if (elem_size == 1)
2812 {
2813 bitMatNot<unsigned char>(
2814 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, bcols, src.data, src.step),
2815 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, bcols, dst.data, dst.step),
2816 mask, num_channels, stream);
2817 }
2818 else if (elem_size == 2)
2819 {
2820 bitMatNot<unsigned short>(
2821 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, bcols, src.data, src.step),
2822 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, bcols, dst.data, dst.step),
2823 mask, num_channels, stream);
2824 }
2825 else if (elem_size == 4)
2826 {
2827 bitMatNot<unsigned int>(
2828 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, bcols, src.data, src.step),
2829 PtrStepSzb(src.rows, bcols, dst.data, dst.step),
2830 mask, num_channels, stream);
2831 }
2832 }
2833}

3098// Binary bitwise logical operations with scalars
3099
3100namespace arithm
3101{
3102 template <typename T> void bitScalarAnd(PtrStepSzb src1, unsigned int src2, PtrStepSzb dst, cudaStream_t stream);
3103 template <typename T> void bitScalarOr(PtrStepSzb src1, unsigned int src2, PtrStepSzb dst, cudaStream_t stream);
3104 template <typename T> void bitScalarXor(PtrStepSzb src1, unsigned int src2, PtrStepSzb dst, cudaStream_t stream);
3105}
3106
3107namespace
3108{
3109 typedef void (*bit_scalar_func_t)(PtrStepSzb src1, unsigned int src2, PtrStepSzb dst, cudaStream_t stream);
3110
3111 template <typename T, bit_scalar_func_t func> struct BitScalar
3112 {
3113 static void call(const GpuMat& src, Scalar sc, GpuMat& dst, cudaStream_t stream)
3114 {
3115 func(src, saturate_cast<T>(sc.val[0]), dst, stream);
3116 }
3117 };
3118
3119 template <bit_scalar_func_t func> struct BitScalar4
3120 {
3121 static void call(const GpuMat& src, Scalar sc, GpuMat& dst, cudaStream_t stream)
3122 {
3123 unsigned int packedVal = 0;
3124
3125 packedVal |= (saturate_cast<unsigned char>(sc.val[0]) & 0xffff);
3126 packedVal |= (saturate_cast<unsigned char>(sc.val[1]) & 0xffff) << 8;
3127 packedVal |= (saturate_cast<unsigned char>(sc.val[2]) & 0xffff) << 16;
3128 packedVal |= (saturate_cast<unsigned char>(sc.val[3]) & 0xffff) << 24;
3129
3130 func(src, packedVal, dst, stream);
3131 }
3132 };
3133
3134 template <int DEPTH, int cn> struct NppBitwiseCFunc
3135 {
3136 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_t npp_t;
3137
3138 typedef NppStatus (*func_t)(const npp_t* pSrc1, int nSrc1Step, const npp_t* pConstants, npp_t* pDst, int nDstStep, NppiSize oSizeROI);
3139 };
3140 template <int DEPTH> struct NppBitwiseCFunc<DEPTH, 1>
3141 {
3142 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_t npp_t;
3143
3144 typedef NppStatus (*func_t)(const npp_t* pSrc1, int nSrc1Step, const npp_t pConstant, npp_t* pDst, int nDstStep, NppiSize oSizeROI);
3145 };
3146
3147 template <int DEPTH, int cn, typename NppBitwiseCFunc<DEPTH, cn>::func_t func> struct NppBitwiseC
3148 {
3149 typedef typename NppBitwiseCFunc<DEPTH, cn>::npp_t npp_t;
3150
3151 static void call(const GpuMat& src, Scalar sc, GpuMat& dst, cudaStream_t stream)
3152 {
3153 NppStreamHandler h(stream);
3154
3155 NppiSize oSizeROI;
3156 oSizeROI.width = src.cols;
3157 oSizeROI.height = src.rows;
3158
3159 const npp_t pConstants[] = {saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[0]), saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[1]), saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[2]), saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[3])};
3160
3161 nppSafeCall( func(src.ptr<npp_t>(), static_cast<int>(src.step), pConstants, dst.ptr<npp_t>(), static_cast<int>(dst.step), oSizeROI) );
3162
3163 if (stream == 0)
3164 cudaSafeCall( cudaDeviceSynchronize() );
3165 }
3166 };
3167 template <int DEPTH, typename NppBitwiseCFunc<DEPTH, 1>::func_t func> struct NppBitwiseC<DEPTH, 1, func>
3168 {
3169 typedef typename NppBitwiseCFunc<DEPTH, 1>::npp_t npp_t;
3170
3171 static void call(const GpuMat& src, Scalar sc, GpuMat& dst, cudaStream_t stream)
3172 {
3173 NppStreamHandler h(stream);
3174
3175 NppiSize oSizeROI;
3176 oSizeROI.width = src.cols;
3177 oSizeROI.height = src.rows;
3178
3179 nppSafeCall( func(src.ptr<npp_t>(), static_cast<int>(src.step), saturate_cast<npp_t>(sc.val[0]), dst.ptr<npp_t>(), static_cast<int>(dst.step), oSizeROI) );
3180
3181 if (stream == 0)
3182 cudaSafeCall( cudaDeviceSynchronize() );
3183 }
3184 };
3185}

3512void cv::gpu::min(const GpuMat& src1, const GpuMat& src2, GpuMat& dst, Stream& s)
3513{
3514 using namespace arithm;
3515
3516 typedef void (*func_t)(PtrStepSzb src1, PtrStepSzb src2, PtrStepSzb dst, cudaStream_t stream);
3517
3518#ifdef OPENCV_TINY_GPU_MODULE
3519 static const func_t funcs[] =
3520 {
3521 minMat<unsigned char>,
3522 0/*minMat<signed char>*/,
3523 0/*minMat<unsigned short>*/,
3524 0/*minMat<short>*/,
3525 0/*minMat<int>*/,
3526 minMat<float>,
3527 0/*minMat<double>*/,
3528 };
3529#else
3530 static const func_t funcs[] =
3531 {
3532 minMat<unsigned char>,
3533 minMat<signed char>,
3534 minMat<unsigned short>,
3535 minMat<short>,
3536 minMat<int>,
3537 minMat<float>,
3538 minMat<double>,
3539 };
3540#endif
3541
3542 const int depth = src1.depth();
3543 const int cn = src1.channels();
3544
3545 CV_Assert( depth <= CV_64F );
3546 CV_Assert( src2.type() == src1.type() && src2.size() == src1.size() );
3547
3548 if (depth == CV_64F)
3549 {
3550 if (!deviceSupports(NATIVE_DOUBLE))

3552 }

3558 PtrStepSzb src1_(src1.rows, src1.cols * cn, src1.data, src1.step);
3559 PtrStepSzb src2_(src1.rows, src1.cols * cn, src2.data, src2.step);
3560 PtrStepSzb dst_(src1.rows, src1.cols * cn, dst.data, dst.step);
3561
3562 if (depth == CV_8U || depth == CV_16U)

3584 {
3585 const int vcols = src1_.cols >> 1;
3586
3587 minMat_v2(PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) src1_.data, src1_.step),
3588 PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) src2_.data, src2_.step),
3589 PtrStepSz<unsigned int>(src1_.rows, vcols, (unsigned int*) dst_.data, dst_.step),
3590 stream);
3591
3592 return;
3593 }
3594 }
3595 }
3596
3597 const func_t func = funcs[depth];
3598
3599 if (!func)
3600 CV_Error(CV_StsUnsupportedFormat, "Unsupported combination of source and destination types");
3601
3602 func(src1_, src2_, dst_, stream);

3862{

3865 CV_Assert( src.channels() == 1 && depth <= CV_64F );

3883 sz.width = src.cols;

3887 dst.ptr<Npp32f>(), static_cast<int>(dst.step), sz, static_cast<Npp32f>(thresh), NPP_CMP_GREATER) );
3888
3889 if (stream == 0)
3890 cudaSafeCall( cudaDeviceSynchronize() );
3891 }
3892 else
3893 {
3894 typedef void (*func_t)(PtrStepSzb src, PtrStepSzb dst, double thresh, double maxVal, int type, cudaStream_t stream);

3904 0/*arithm::threshold<double>*/
3905 };
3906#else
3907 static const func_t funcs[] =
3908 {
3909 arithm::threshold<unsigned char>,
3910 arithm::threshold<signed char>,

3916 };

3921 CV_Error(CV_StsNotImplemented, "not available in tiny build");

3978 CV_Error(CV_StsUnsupportedFormat, "The device doesn't support double");
3979 }
3980
3981 const func_t func = funcs[depth];
3982 if (!func)
3983 CV_Error(CV_StsNotImplemented, "not available in tiny build");
3984
3985 dst.create(src.size(), src.type());
3986
3987 PtrStepSzb src_(src.rows, src.cols * cn, src.data, src.step);
3988 PtrStepSzb dst_(src.rows, src.cols * cn, dst.data, dst.step);
3989
3990 func(src_, power, dst_, StreamAccessor::getStream(stream));
3991}

3995
3996namespace
3997{
3998 template <int DEPTH> struct NppAlphaCompFunc
3999 {
4000 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_t npp_t;
4001
4002 typedef NppStatus (*func_t)(const npp_t* pSrc1, int nSrc1Step, const npp_t* pSrc2, int nSrc2Step, npp_t* pDst, int nDstStep, NppiSize oSizeROI, NppiAlphaOp eAlphaOp);
4003 };
4004
4005 template <int DEPTH, typename NppAlphaCompFunc<DEPTH>::func_t func> struct NppAlphaComp
4006 {
4007 typedef typename NppTypeTraits<DEPTH>::npp_t npp_t;
4008
4009 static void call(const GpuMat& img1, const GpuMat& img2, GpuMat& dst, NppiAlphaOp eAlphaOp, cudaStream_t stream)
4010 {
4011 NppStreamHandler h(stream);
4012
4013 NppiSize oSizeROI;
4014 oSizeROI.width = img1.cols;
4015 oSizeROI.height = img2.rows;
4016
4017 nppSafeCall( func(img1.ptr<npp_t>(), static_cast<int>(img1.step), img2.ptr<npp_t>(), static_cast<int>(img2.step),
4018 dst.ptr<npp_t>(), static_cast<int>(dst.step), oSizeROI, eAlphaOp) );
4019
4020 if (stream == 0)
4021 cudaSafeCall( cudaDeviceSynchronize() );
4022 }
4023 };
4024}

4026void cv::gpu::alphaComp(const GpuMat& img1, const GpuMat& img2, GpuMat& dst, int alpha_op, Stream& stream)
4027{
4028 static const NppiAlphaOp npp_alpha_ops[] = {
4029 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_OVER,
4030 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_IN,
4031 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_OUT,
4032 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_ATOP,
4033 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_XOR,
4034 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_PLUS,
4035 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_OVER_PREMUL,
4036 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_IN_PREMUL,
4037 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_OUT_PREMUL,
4038 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_ATOP_PREMUL,
4039 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_XOR_PREMUL,
4040 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_PLUS_PREMUL,
4041 NPPI_OP_ALPHA_PREMUL
4042 };
4043
4044 typedef void (*func_t)(const GpuMat& img1, const GpuMat& img2, GpuMat& dst, NppiAlphaOp eAlphaOp, cudaStream_t stream);
4045
4046 static const func_t funcs[] =
4047 {
4048 NppAlphaComp<CV_8U, nppiAlphaComp_8u_AC4R>::call,
4049 0,
4050 NppAlphaComp<CV_16U, nppiAlphaComp_16u_AC4R>::call,
4051 0,
4052 NppAlphaComp<CV_32S, nppiAlphaComp_32s_AC4R>::call,
4053 NppAlphaComp<CV_32F, nppiAlphaComp_32f_AC4R>::call
4054 };
4055
4056 CV_Assert( img1.type() == CV_8UC4 || img1.type() == CV_16UC4 || img1.type() == CV_32SC4 || img1.type() == CV_32FC4 );
4057 CV_Assert( img1.size() == img2.size() && img1.type() == img2.type() );
4058
4059 dst.create(img1.size(), img1.type());
4060
4061 const func_t func = funcs[img1.depth()];
4062
4063 func(img1, img2, dst, npp_alpha_ops[alpha_op], StreamAccessor::getStream(stream));
4064}
